There are different size of heading that you can use while , there are series of sizes like <h1></h1> , <h2> </h2>, <hn> </hn> and so on .
There is different thing which called making paragraph , for which syntax is <p> </p> , 
coloring a sentence or word  - <p style = "color = color_name ;">  here the text that you want to change color </p>  .

